data.description: Charming and affordable ranch with lake privileges to Cass Lake. 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, 2 car garage located in West Bloomfield Schools. The current owner enjoys the convenience of a boat slip on Cass Lake, facilitated through the Cass Lakeside Community Association (CLCA) via Zox Neighborhood. Inquire for more details about CLCA Dock Regulations. Return home from the lake and relax in the three-seasons room with a natural fireplace that provides additional functionality and living space. The seller has already connected and paid to connect to the sewer system. Water and community building access are included with the annual HOA fee. Embrace the "lake life" this summer and schedule a private showing today to discover all the features this home offers.
